# Workflow: Self Review (Before PR)

- [ ] Scope is focused and matches the spec/work item.
- [ ] No accidental secrets committed.
- [ ] No broken/unreferenced imports, dead code, or debug prints.
- [ ] Tests updated for behaviour changes.
- [ ] Commands run:
  - [ ] Format: `{{format_cmd}}`
  - [ ] Lint: `{{lint_cmd}}`
  - [ ] Test: `{{test_cmd}}`
- [ ] PR description includes verification steps and rollback notes.

